            <listitem>
              <para><xref linkend="pro.ha.config.hawk.history.explorer.offline"
                /> describes a new &hawk; function to view and analyze the
                transitions of clusters that you are currently not connected to
                (Fate#313354).</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
              <para>Used example of setting up an NFS server to demonstrate use
                of &hawk; <guimenu>Cluster Setup Wizard</guimenu>
                (Fate#315163). See <xref linkend="pro.ha.config.hawk.wizard"
                />.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
              <para>The description of all &hawk; functions that are related
                to &geo; clusters has been moved to a separate document. See
                the new <citetitle>&hageo; &geoquick;</citetitle>,
                available from &suse-onlinedoc;.</para>
            </listitem>
          </itemizedlist>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

